<%= render "shared/navbar-home" %>
<div class="banner" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.3),rgba(0,0,0,0.3)), url('./assets/banner.png');">

  <div class="row justify-content-center" style="margin-top: 120px">
    <div class="search-bar col-12 col-lg-6">
      <div>
        <h5 class="search-header" style="font-weight: bold">Where do you want to work?</h5>
        <%= form_tag spaces_path, class: "search-container", method: :get do %>
           <%= text_field_tag :location,
               params[:location],
               placeholder: "", class: "form-control search", autofocus: true
            %>
          <div class="input-group-append">
            <button class="button-search" type="submit"><i class="fas fa-search search"></i></button>
          </div>
         <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

  <div class="home-contents">
    <div class="home-container-1">
      <div>
        <h2>Explore HUBert</h2>
        <p>HUBert offers plenty of differnt home office and coworking variations – go and check them out. </p>
      </div>

      <div class="cards">
        <div class="card-category" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.3), rgba(0,0,0,0.3)), url(https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lewagon/fullstack-images/master/uikit/breakfast.jpg)">
          Private spaces
        </div>

        <div class="card-category" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.3), rgba(0,0,0,0.3)), url(https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lewagon/fullstack-images/master/uikit/lunch.jpg)">
          Community spaces
        </div>

        <div class="card-category" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.3), rgba(0,0,0,0.3)), url(https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lewagon/fullstack-images/master/uikit/dinner.jpg)">
          Corporate spaces
        </div>

        <div class="card-category" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.3), rgba(0,0,0,0.3)), url(https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lewagon/fullstack-images/master/uikit/dinner.jpg)">
          Professional spaces
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  <div class="home-container-2">
    <div>
      <h2>How does HUBert work and what’s in for you?</h2>
      <p>HUBert is designed to leverage existing spaces and create new communities in the local neighborhoods. For example, a private individual who has more space than he or she actually needs for his or her own home office can offer a home office space to a neighbor who has a need but little private space. In addition, operators of commercial coworking spaces, can achieve better occupancy of the workspaces they offer, by providing home office space to individuals who live nearby. In addition, companies that have a larger office building capacity than they actually need can rent out the excess workspace to private individuals through HUBert. We're building on local synergies between individuals and individuals and businesses. Space is plentiful - it's just a question of how we use it.</p>
    </div>
    <%= image_tag('Big_Card.png') %>
  </div>

  <div class="home-container-3">
    <div>
      <h2>Private coworking spaces</h2>
      <p>Use the available private space we have. Learn more about your neighborhood and foster community as well.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="home-spaces">
      <% @private_spaces.limit(5).each do |space| %>
      <%= link_to space_path(space.id, :location => params[:location]) do %>
        <div class="card card-grid">
          <% if space.photo.attached? %>
            <%= cl_image_tag space.photo.key, crop: :fill %>
          <% end %>
          <div class="card-body">
            <p class="card-spacetype"><%= space.space_type %></p>
            <h5 class="card-title"><%= space.title %></h5>
            <div class="card-details">
              <p class="card-location"><%= space.location %></p>
              <p class="card-price"><%= space.price_per_month %> €<span style="font-size: 0.7rem"> per month</span></p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      <% end %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="home-container-4">
    <div>
      <h2>Community coworking spaces</h2>
      <p>Be part of an ecosystem of all types of workers in a porfessional coworking space as part of your home office. Find one next to your home.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="home-spaces">
      <% @community_spaces.limit(5).each do |space| %>
